translation.Name: Buak_Note_02
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: Like the watered down character I am, I just watched as it happened with a fist full of money, you see? There’s no room for my old self anymore in this world, wolves and sheep, but I don’t enjoy being a wolf. It’s a facade, it all is, and always will be! It all looked so fake, but it felt so real, there’s no telling it apart, it felt like a movie but I was living my own life. Why do I do this? To protect myself? I need to find some better cases to work on.
